c: 14
v: 18
t: "“Fanizo la amene sadakhulupirire Mbuye wawo, zochita zawo (zabwino zomwe sadzalipidwa nazo chabwino chilichonse chifukwa chakuti sadazichite pofuna kukondweretsa Allah) zili ngati phulusa lomwe likuulutsidwa ndi mphepo ya mkuntho; ndipo sadzatha kupindula chilichonse pa zimene adachita, uko ndikutaika konka nako kutali (ndi choonadi)"